"    </p>",
"    <p>",
"     <a class=\"medical medical_basics\" href=\"mobipreview.htm?15/49/16147?source=see_link\">",
"      Patient information: Treatment for type 2 diabetes (The Basics)",
"     </a>",
"     <br/>",
